## Package-Specific Exclusions

### Wirehair Compiled Binaries
/src/Drivers/wirehair_build/
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib
*.a
*.lib
*.o

### Test Fixtures and Generated Files
/tests/fixtures/generated/
/tests/fixtures/*.mp4
/tests/fixtures/*.avi
/tests/fixtures/*.mov
!tests/fixtures/.gitkeep
tests/output/
tests/coverage/

### OAuth and Credentials
/oauth-credentials.json
youtube-credentials.json
*.pem
*.key
!config/youtube-storage.php

### Binary Paths (Auto-detected)
ffmpeg
ffprobe
yt-dlp
wirehair.so
wirehair.dll
wirehair.dylib

### Cache and Runtime
.cache/
.runtime/
*.cache

